casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Richard Andrew TALLENT, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158961
COA: 346395 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 8, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion of defendant-appellant to file a supplemental appendix to his application for leave to appeal is GRANTED. The supplemental appendix submitted on March 5, 2019, is accepted for filing.
